      <name>Romeo &amp; Juliet</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<b>Romeo &amp; Juliet</b><br><i>Theatre</i><br>Wed 18th Mar – Sat 20th Jun<br>The Harold Pinter Theatre, West End<br>from £20 per ticket<br><br>Shakespeare’s famous love story returns to the West End, directed by Robert Icke, featuring Sadie Sink as Juliet and Noah Jupe as Romeo in an emotionally charged production.<br><br><a href="https://www.designmynight.com/london/whats-on/theatre/romeo-and-juliet-at-the-harold-pinter-theatre">More info / tickets</a>]]></description>
